# 詞: 陰功

1. 佢為咗個計劃日日加班，真係陰功。 (He works overtime every day for the project. It's really hard on him.)
2. 個細路仔要自己照顧自己，真係陰功。 (The little kid has to take care of himself. It's really hard on him.)
3. 佢病到咁重都要返工，真係陰功。 (He has to go to work even though he's very sick. It's really hard on him.)
4. 個老人家要自己煮飯洗衫，真係陰功。 (The elderly person has to cook and do laundry by themselves. It's really hard on them.)
5. 佢為咗儲錢去旅行，連飯都唔食，真係陰功。 (He doesn't even eat to save money for the trip. It's really hard on him.)
6. 個學生要兼顧學業同兼職，真係陰功。 (The student has to balance studies and part-time work. It's really hard on them.)
7. 佢為咗照顧個病嘅家人，連覺都唔瞓，真係陰功。 (He doesn't sleep to take care of his sick family member. It's really hard on him.)
8. 個工人要日日搬重嘢，真係陰功。 (The worker has to carry heavy things every day. It's really hard on them.)
9. 佢為咗追夢，連屋企人都唔理，真係陰功。 (He neglects his family for the sake of chasing his dreams. It's really hard on him.)
10. 個媽媽要照顧成家，連休息時間都冇，真係陰功。 (The mother has to take care of the whole family without any rest time. It's really hard on her.) [end of text]


